11:
MARVELOUS! Most impressive! How
would you feel about a position at
PBC?
14:
Why do I feel like I'd immediately be
exploited for my labor?
17:
Not at all! At PBC, results are all that
matter, and those who can deliver
are rewarded... handsomely.
19:
More importantly, I've triangulated
Bulleta's position. Shall we?
29:
Oh, and one more thing! PBC's
mental health services for any
incurred trauma on the job are also
first-class!
33:
I'm... just gonna leave that alone.
Either way, we appreciate the help.
38:
Excellent. Even if Miss Freedom can't
get the job done, we've got a new
backup plan.
40:
I can already smell the profits!
Now all I need to do is... a little this...
a little that... Heh-heh...
53:
Yeah, I've had enough... of you!
I'm gonna make this one a brandy,
so... fill 'er up!
55:
I'm cutting you off. Please
understand.
60:
It seems that alcohol is also sold as
AdTaste here.
68:
I don't even know how I'm supposed
to look at her anymore...
70: The same way you always have.
74:
I just can't believe it. Why would she
lie to me this whole time?
77: I'm... I'm sure she has her reasons.
80:
It's like... were we ever even really
friends?
89: I don't know how Love feels, but...
91:
How you feel about her is, well,
entirely up to you.
95:
Love... I always thought of her as a
friend.
97:
We've been partners since the very
beginning. I just can't imagine
troubleshooting without her by my
side, you know?
100: Then that's good enough, isn't it?
104:
Indeed. Even the best of friends may
clash at times—whether it be with
words or blades.
107:
Surely there's more to the whole
story that we don't know about too,
right?
110:
The best way to find out would be to
talk to her directly.
117: She said it was curtains for us, but...
121:
This battle ain't over until I say it's
over.
125:
'Cuz this freedom blaster's still
loaded, baby!
128:
And I'm blasting that piece of crap
throne of hers into smithereens—just
you watch!
133:
Sounds like someone's made up
their mind!
138:
The time for games is over. I'm
gonna show her just how serious I
can be when it comes down to it.
144:
Marvelous! If you're gonna go out,
might as well go out with the
biggest bang possible, I always say!
148:
And do I have the PERFECT service
pack just for the occasion. What do
you say?
154:
Now THAT'S what I call destruction!
It's amazing what you can get away
with when you tell people you're
filming a movie!
159:
You guys keep up the diversion
while I look for Love. Got it?
162:
Marvelous! And if you need me, I'll
be retreati—I mean, OVERSEEING the
operation from my command
center!
168: *sigh* Just try not to get in our way.
181:
I promised her that we'd talk it
out—and I don't break my promises!
